Third-party components
----------------------
This project orchestrates the following components, which it does not modify or
redistribute (they are pulled as upstream container images / packages at deploy time):

- SearXNG — https://github.com/searxng/searxng — AGPL-3.0-or-later.
  Run as an unmodified upstream container for search discovery. Only configuration
  (searxng/settings.yml) is included in this repository.

Phase 1 of this project used ihor-sokoliuk/mcp-searxng (MIT) as the MCP layer; it
has since been replaced by the in-repo gateway/ router.
